works.description: Porsche Design has never failed to turn heads with its range of luxury accessories. This time, the luxury brand has rolled out a gilded edition of its famous P’9522 mobile phone. The Porsche Design’s P’9522 has already won the Good Design Award at the 59th Good Design Award in 2009 and has received the iF Product Design Award’s highest accolade in 2010. The new Porsche Design P’9522 Gold Limited Edition flaunts gold plated 5-micron casing and black mineral glass.
